About Activity Editor EO
This tool is an open-source utility for editing Eudemons Online activity configuration files and task scripts. It provides an easy-to-use interface for modifying playexplain.ini, activitycalendarnew.ini, and related database values.
Feel free to contribute or report issues on GitHub: For questions or support, you can also contact me on Facebook:
